South Africa is a wonderful country. Sure it has its fair share of issues, just like any country. What we saw over the last few weeks is not the South Africa we love and know. What you see in this video is the true South African spirit. Come visit us when you can, you won’t be sorry you did. Once it gets in your blood you’ll be back again and again for more!
